{"tid":1834104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】消息指本港錄首宗確診個案　傳經高鐵來港","createTime":"2020-01-22T09:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T10:17:07.000Z","uid":73092,"like":94,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"4714f2ccd4f17428b512c063b562daa79ad34de2","tid":1834104,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:02:21.000Z","msg":"武漢新型冠狀病毒在全球開始擴散，由去年底至昨午 12 時，本港錄得 106 宗個案。據多名消息人士向《立場新聞》透露，本港今日下午錄得首宗確診個案。據消息人士指，本港發現首宗武漢新型冠狀病毒確診個案，在伊利沙伯醫院留醫。另外，據公立醫院知情人士透露，該名男病人經高鐵來香港。<br />\n<br />\n立場新聞"},{"pid":"a9800eecf853ff6d67f6c546049c45fa1d75d708","tid":1834104,"uid":9305,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:02:53.000Z","msg":"鳩鐵又贏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c04d287763f5d60422ba78edafa40417c9379b","tid":1834104,"uid":8014,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:02:57.000Z","msg":"送大禮"},{"pid":"d8e15371177276dfc68a7e377ac225d93bc9c456","tid":1834104,"uid":345562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e321b3eae18039bf0244ebd977f006b1030d385","tid":1834104,"uid":121259,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:03:07.000Z","msg":"香港都失守啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c33b325dce6370bed73f5f1f5c1a2a709604bd6","tid":1834104,"uid":35574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63120a53b2733fef184f864dfbf5dd12152dfa6","tid":1834104,"uid":37869,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:03:07.000Z","msg":"張建宗：冇事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />